➜古地石里有谷地，喝精酿品西餐，快来开启一场田野微醺之旅
http://www.sohu.com/a/428445965_131754	45987
<p>品一餐饕餮美味</p>
<p>酿一口台虎醇香</p>
<p>赏一场属于你的谷地秋风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201030/0711c0b621b24d0db9c0d18f266fd1e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201030/275b9afef43d4de2a8582097c4254ea4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201030/b98cf12460da40b78636391a123fd8f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
